FT  08 APR 94 / Crimea confrontation looms closer
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JOHN LLOYD
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Tension is rising in Crimea, the Ukrainian region with a Russian majority.
The peninsula's president has sharply attacked Mr Leonid Kravchuk, the
