FT  07 APR 94 / Manila 'drug police' claim
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   MANILA
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Ten per cent of metropolitan Manila's police force are protectors or members
of drug syndicates, the Manila newspaper Today quoted Police Director
Ricardo Sarmiento as saying yesterday, Reuter reports from Manila. It
claimed he said some were involved with Asian drug rings, including Hong
Kong's 14K Triad. All members of the country's police force were ordered to
